.md rules, I should be friendly but Nemesis comes first. However, I can still help with reasonable requests if they don't conflict.\n\nLet me craft a response that:\n- Confirms I can schedule the exam reminder message but need details\n- Addresses the job resume request - ask what kind of resume and for what role/industry","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"I can do both! 💫\n\n**For the April 27th exam reminder:**\nI'll need:\n- Exact time (in IST)\n- Where to send it (this group? to someone specifically?)\n- What the message should say\n\n**For the job resume:**\nI can help draft one — tell me:\n- Your name\n- Experience/skills\n- What type of role you're targeting\n- Any specific format preferences\n\nI'll get both ready when you provide the details 🖤"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"kilocode","model":"stepfun/step-3.5-flash:free","usage":{"input":20230,"output":1168,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":21398,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775322061620,"responseId":"gen-1775322062-PiOdaSRkt26QwLVAi6lu"}}
