{"type":"message","id":"1a8021d0","parentId":"1d10a32e","timestamp":"2026-04-04T17:10:06.271Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking about how I will send the resume. They want to know the format or method. Since I'm an AI assistant, I can draft the resume content and send it as a message in the group chat (or DM if they prefer). The resume would be in text format, possibly with formatting like bold headings, bullet points, etc.\n\nI should explain:\n- I'll draft the resume content\n- I'll send it as a formatted text message (can include markdown-like formatting)\n- They can copy-paste it into a document or use it directly\n- If they want a file (PDF/DOCX), that would require additional steps (maybe I can generate a text file they can convert)\n\nI should ask for their details first to actually create the resume.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"I'll draft it right here in the chat as formatted text — you can copy-paste it into a document or send it directly wherever you need.\n\nIf you want a PDF/DOCX file instead, I can create the file in my workspace and you can grab it.\n\nEither way works — which do you prefer? And don't forget to share your details (name, experience, skills, target role) so I can actually write it 😉"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"kilocode","model":"stepfun/step-3.5-flash:free","usage":{"input":22931,"output":433,"cacheRead":1024,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":24388,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775322595362,"responseId":"gen-1775322595-NrIAWayTByjufAOTaDOu"}}
